# Sales Data Dictionary

## Dataset Overview

**File**: Sales_Data.xlsx  
**Records**: 962 transactions  
**Time Period**: 2023 sales data  
**Business Domain**: Coffee and Tea retail sales  

## Field Definitions

| Field Name | Data Type | Description | Example Values | Validation Rules |
|------------|-----------|-------------|----------------|------------------|
| Order ID | String | Unique transaction identifier | TCSTORD1, TCSTORD2 | Required, Unique, Format: TCSTORD + Number |
| Date | Date | Transaction date | 2023-01-02 | Required, Valid date format (YYYY-MM-DD) |
| Product | String | Product name | Espresso Energizer, Zen Green Tea | Required, Must be from product catalog |
| Category | String | Product category | Coffee, Tea | Required, Limited to: Coffee, Tea |
| State | String | Customer state | Michigan, Georgia | Required, Valid US state name |
| Units Sold | Integer | Quantity purchased | 2, 3, 5 | Required, Positive integer |
| Unit Price | Decimal | Price per unit | 2.50, 3.80 | Required, Positive number with 2 decimals |
| Sales | Decimal | Total sale amount | 7.50, 11.40 | Required, Calculated: Units Sold × Unit Price |

